snippet.title: YoRHa 2B Angel
snippet.description:
On this channel you will find original music, soundtracks from popular games. You can find complete music playlists of such games as Warframe, Death Stranding, Deus Ex, Metal Gear Solid  and others. Music from the Anime - Evangelion,  Ghost In The Shell, Kill la Kill and others. If you like dramatic and emotional music (Instrumental) that causes goosebumps, then subscribe to the channel. 

Non-Profit Channel.
